</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Keith Park in front of his Hurricane OK-2 on <a href="/wiki/Malta" title="Malta">Malta</a> in 1942</p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Air_Chf_Mshl_Leigh-Mallory.jpg" class="image" title="Air Chf Mshl Leigh-Mallory.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Air_Chf_Mshl_Leigh-Mallory.jpg/112px-Air_Chf_Mshl_Leigh-Mallory.jpg" width="112" height="119" border="0" /></a></div>
